@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wlghxi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.16 * (wp.cos(v0 + 0.52) - (v2 + 0.59 - tmp + 0.66)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(0.68) - wp.abs((tmp + 0.02 + v1 + 0.05)))
    v2 = (0.03 / 0.52)
    v2 = v0
    v2 = v1
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
